                            <comment id="16629803" author="stephenc" created="Thu, 27 Sep 2018 06:13:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IIRC it was hard enough getting interest to publish releases... but were back in the mists of time&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16630699" author="jay.zhuang" created="Thu, 27 Sep 2018 16:30:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do you think the&#160;change should go to trunk only or other branches too?&lt;br/&gt;
I would prefer branches from 2.2, as we might have snapshot artifacts for all active branches.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16631185" author="michaelsembwever" created="Thu, 27 Sep 2018 23:27:29 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Do you think the change should go to trunk only or other branches too?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m thinking only trunk to begin with, as that&apos;s where the current need is. We also don&apos;t know how this will work, and it might be better to iron out wrinkles against just trunk first, and back-port it later if a definite need arises. That&apos;s my opinion, otherwise easy.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
